Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}现在起不要直视他们的脸{\r}\N{\fs16}Now, do not look at their faces.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}这会让人产生怜悯与同情之心{\r}\N{\fs16}That can trigger feelings and emotions,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}而在《文明时代2.0: 怪人的崛起》中那是行不通的{\r}\N{\fs16}which have no place in Civilization 2.0: Rise of the Weirdos.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}我已经解决了此类问题{\r}\N{\fs16}I may have solved that problem.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}这是我改装的步枪瞄准仪{\r}\N{\fs16}This rifle scope I modified{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}它会使任何一张人脸看起来都充满危险和攻击性{\r}\N{\fs16}makes any human face look dangerous and threatening.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}为什么要将他们全部击毙?{\r}\N{\fs16}Why do we have to shoot them at all?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}你能用刀达到同样效果?{\r}\N{\fs16}Are you that good with a knife?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}不 我想要帮助那些没做准备的人{\r}\N{\fs16}No! I want to help the people who didn't prepare.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}你为什么要向我开枪?{\r}\N{\fs16}What'd you shoot me for?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}你在想我是不是疯了 是不是?{\r}\N{\fs16}You were thinking I'd gone mad with power, weren't you?!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}没有 但我现在这么想了{\r}\N{\fs16}I wasn't, but I am now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}天啊 什么情况?{\r}\N{\fs16}Oh, God, now what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}每次你一大早把我们吵醒{\r}\N{\fs16}Every time you wake us up early in the morning,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}不是要去教堂 就是要我们改变身份{\r}\N{\fs16}it's either church or we have to change our identities.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}别乱想 Mary Ellen{\r}\N{\fs16}Don't be silly, Mary Ellen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}我们现在得离开这个地方{\r}\N{\fs16}Now we're going to leave this place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}对不起了 Bart{\r}\N{\fs16}I'm sorry, Bart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}我知道你交了一个露营女朋友{\r}\N{\fs16}I know you've made a bug-out camp girlfriend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}我得跟你说老实话{\r}\N{\fs16}I've got to be honest with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}那只是一袋米 我在上面画了张脸而已{\r}\N{\fs16}It was just a bag of rice I drew a face on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}好米还是糙米?{\r}\N{\fs16}White rice or brown?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}我没注意过{\r}\N{\fs16}I never noticed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}好孩子{\r}\N{\fs16}Good boy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}我们要将这些补给品运回到春田镇{\r}\N{\fs16}So we'll take these supplies back to Springfield{\r}
