Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs10\fn华文中宋\shad0\bord0\c&H010101&\pos(183,103)}净水药片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs10\fn华文中宋\shad0\bord0\c&H010101&\pos(264,176)}自杀药片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs10\fn华文中宋\shad0\bord0\c&H010101&\pos(266,196)}A片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}那儿的人急需要{\r}\N{\fs16}where they're needed most.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}你是个大好人 Homer Simpson{\r}\N{\fs16}You're a good man, Homer Simpson.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}你说你把警报器的线切断了啊{\r}\N{\fs16}You said you cut the wires to the alarm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}我确实是把什么东西的线给切断了{\r}\N{\fs16}Hmm, I cut the wires to something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}50年冰淇淋供给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}听好 大家伙儿 都把眼睛盯准了{\r}\N{\fs16}Okay everybody, keep your eyes peeled{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}找一个不发亮的里程标 标着"23""36"还是多少的{\r}\N{\fs16}for an unlit mile post marked "23" or "36" or something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}如果我们错过了就死定了{\r}\N{\fs16}If we miss it, we're dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}爸爸 后面有灯光跟着我们{\r}\N{\fs16}Dad, there are lights following us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}怎么可能? 我把所有的汽油都拿走了啊{\r}\N{\fs16}How can that be? I took every last can of gas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}好了 大家放松{\r}\N{\fs16}Now, everyone relax{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}假装我们是要撞上一堵软砖墙{\r}\N{\fs16}and pretend we're about to be hit by a soft brick wall.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}别挡路 玉米{\r}\N{\fs16}Out of our way, corn!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}春田镇饥饿的人们{\r}\N{\fs16}The starving people of Springfield{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}正迫切等待我们的罐装玉米 玉米片...{\r}\N{\fs16}are desperately in need of our delivery of canned corn,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}还有速冻玉米粒火速送到呢{\r}\N{\fs16}corn flakes and flash frozen corn niblets!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}我为你感到骄傲{\r}\N{\fs16}I'm proud of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}社会也许崩溃了 但是我们的道德永存{\r}\N{\fs16}Society may have crumbled, but our decency hasn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}现在就去拯救痛苦的灵魂 {\r}\N{\fs16}Now to save these sorry souls{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}让他们摆脱混乱饥饿以及为了繁衍而做爱的生活{\r}\N{\fs16}from a life of anarchy, starvation and having sex for procreation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}一切都很正常{\r}\N{\fs16}Oh, everything's normal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}世界没有毁灭{\r}\N{\fs16}The world didn't end!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}老爸 你说过人们会互饮对方的血的{\r}\N{\fs16}Dad, you said people would be drinking each other's blood.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an8}1984年战争电影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}你把《赤色黎明》看上13遍也会这么说的{\r}\N{\fs16}You got to watch a VHS copy of Red Dawn 13 times!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}别再抱怨了{\r}\N{\fs16}Stop complaining!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}不是发生电磁冲击波了吗?{\r}\N{\fs16}What happened with the E.M.P.?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}春田镇只是停了会儿电{\r}\N{\fs16}Only Springfield lost power,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}几天之后就来电了{\r}\N{\fs16}you see, and after a few days, it came back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}还比以前更亮堂了{\r}\N{\fs16}Maybe a little bit brighter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}而且邻里间互帮互助的精神也涌现出来了{\r}\N{\fs16}And the spirit of neighborly cooperation broke out{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}好像所有暴脾气的怪人都走了似的{\r}\N{\fs16}as if all the weird, angry people had left.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}社会没有崩溃?{\r}\N{\fs16}Then society didn't crumble?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}动物园里的动物没被吃掉?{\r}\N{\fs16}The zoo animals weren't eaten?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}没 好吧 是有那么几只{\r}\N{\fs16}No-- well, a couple.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}这次没有发生的灾难才是大灾难{\r}\N{\fs16}This non-disaster is a catastrophe!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}这世界没有毁灭 你就那么失望{\r}\N{\fs16}Are you really so disappointed the world didn't end,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}那么想证明你是对的?{\r}\N{\fs16}just so you could be proven right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}不是的 不是的 {\r}\N{\fs16}No, no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}只是因为 在新世界里{\r}\N{\fs16}It's just that, in the new world,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}我也许能成为一个大人物{\r}\N{\fs16}I would have been a big shot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}等不了多久的{\r}\N{\fs16}Well, not for long.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}我和其他人正在商量{\r}\N{\fs16}Me and the others were planning{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}推翻你再把你禁闭在洞穴里{\r}\N{\fs16}to overthrow you and seal you in a cave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}是嘛 但是你并不知道{\r}\N{\fs16}Yeah, but what you didn't know{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}我会把你们所有的饮用水都下毒{\r}\N{\fs16}was I was gonna poison all your drinking water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}所以我现在只喝自己的尿{\r}\N{\fs16}Which is why I'm only drinking my own urine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}各位 难道大家没发觉就算是一个不完美的社会{\r}\N{\fs16}Guys, can't you see that even an imperfect society{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}也比创造一个野蛮愚昧的新社会要好吗?{\r}\N{\fs16}is better than the savagery of creating a new one?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}我很高兴我们还拥有文明{\r}\N{\fs16}I for one am glad we're stuck with civilization,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}而且我认为我们还会拥有很长很长的时间{\r}\N{\fs16}and I think we will be for a long, long time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}我饿了{\r}\N{\fs16}I'm hungry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}听着 你可以现在就吃薯片{\r}\N{\fs16}Look, you can have potato chips now,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}或者再等个十分钟{\r}\N{\fs16}or if you wait ten minutes,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}就能随心所欲地吃脑子了{\r}\N{\fs16}you can have all the brains you can eat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00FFFF&}我两样都要{\r}\N{\fs16}I want both.{\r}
